Ɔbenfo Aba. A. Bentil Andam yɛ Ghana ni abɔdeɛ mu nyansapɛ ne fa ɛhwɛ mfidi dwuma ne ahoɔden kunini.  Yɛwoo no wɔ afe apem ahankorɔn aduonan nwɔtwe (1948) mu. Ɔbɛyɛɛ panin a ɔda kuo ah ɛhwɛ abɔdeɛ mu nyansapɛ sua soɔ wɔ Ghana mu wɔ 2017-2019. Ɔno ne Ghana nii ɔbaa ah odii kan nyaa abɔdin wɔ abɔdeɛmu nyansapɛ sua ne fa ɛhwɛ mfidi dwuma ne ahoɔdenneɛ mu.<ref>https://www.ghanabusinessnews.com/2016/03/12/ghanas-first-female-physicist-calls-for-gender-parity-in-science/</ref>

== Abrabɔ nne nteteɛ ==
Yɛwoo Aba afe 1948 mu wɔ Adwumako kɔkɔben wɔ ɔman Ghana mu. Ɔkɔɔ ne ntoasoɔ sukuu wɔ Mfantseman sukuupɔn (Mfantseman Girls SHS). Na ɔkɔɔ Oguaa sukuupɔn (UCC) wɔ afe 1969 na owiee n'adesua 1973, Ɛhɔ na ɔnyaa n'abɔdin krataa wɔ abɔdeɛmu nyansapɛ ne fǎ a ɛhwɛ mfididwuma ne ahoɔden ɛne nkotaabuo mu
